questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide premium plugins and themes?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, elementor pro and crocoblock premium plugin is free in my services.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I edit my site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You can do whatever you want when I deliver the site.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What kind of services can I get from here?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
You can design any type of wordpress website using elementor pro and crocoblock , 
duplicate website, redesign website, elementor website, elementor pro website, wordpress website, replicate website Using elementor pro page builder.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How can I trust you?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
I provide 100% customer satisfaction, I am an wordpress and elementor pro expert, 
I create Clone Websites in a Pixel Perfect way with my maximum talent using Wordpress and elementor  pro.
I also specialize in creating Elementor Websites and Elementor Pro websites.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I get a responsive desktop/tab/mobile- friendly design?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, websites will be completely 100% Responsive and mobile friendly for every kind of device.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What should I do in the beginning?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Domain and Hosting, basic something information of your business, business logo, color scheme, pages names and content, 
otherwise similar website link that you like very much.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Where I can get Domain/Hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You can get these two things from GoDaddy, Blue Host, or HostGator, Name Cheap. These are the best in the market.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I contact you anytime and ask anything?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes sure. contact me anytime and I will answer all the questions.
